  <title>Cogl.Framebuffer.prototype.clear</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function clear(buffers: Number(gulong), color: <link xref="Cogl.Color">Cogl.Color</link>): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for cogl_framebuffer_clear()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Clears all the auxiliary buffers identified in the <code>buffers</code> mask, and if
that includes the color buffer then the specified <code>color</code> is used.</p>
  <p>Since 1.8</p>
<terms>
<item>
<title><code>buffers</code></title>
  <p>A mask of <link xref="Cogl.BufferBit"/>&lt;!-- --&gt;'s identifying which auxiliary
  buffers to clear</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>color</code></title>
  <p>The color to clear the color buffer too if specified in
        <code>buffers</code>.</p>
</item>
